  "2284650": {
    "name": "Sweet Dreams Dahlia",
    "steam_appid": 2284650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/e0b2b6bceb9fc11fcdb70ee0a79313af.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/e0b2b6bceb9fc11fcdb70ee0a79313af.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/e0b2b6bceb9fc11fcdb70ee0a79313af.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扮演Dahlia和Axo，相互帮助，探索这场史诗般的冒险。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dahlia从永恒的睡眠中醒来，失去了记忆。王国已被Crystal Plague摧毁。与她的飞行伙伴Axo一起，他们必须探索古老的Amary世界，战斗腐化的生物，躲避致命的陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开Dahlia的真实身份，揭开王国覆灭的谜团，只有这样，才能重写它的命运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong>一个辽阔而美丽的世界，解开四个不同种族的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗</strong>对抗强大的敌人和Boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级</strong>Dahlia和Axo的技能，应对每一个挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/126022a935acb780da0deac42ca118bd.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/126022a935acb780da0deac42ca118bd.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/126022a935acb780da0deac42ca118bd.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/f6326c337a4768eecd5f02b272fd43d2.avif?t=1770061582\" width=276 height=123 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索神秘的Amary世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dahlia通过一个不太可能的盟友获得自由，发现自己被敌人包围。她偶然发现了一艘破损的船，Dahlia和Axo在这里形成了一个惊人的共生关系。现在，他们一起将解锁王国的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们探索了一个由四个不同种族组成的世界。由于Crystal Plague的爆发，它们的土地已被毁坏，现在所有公民都变成了行尸走肉，看到Dahlia和Axo就会攻击他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是什么触发了这些敌人的反应？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/2dfa70a7c2c4a4da6572613f16873196.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/2dfa70a7c2c4a4da6572613f16873196.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/2dfa70a7c2c4a4da6572613f16873196.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/4774b022bcfc03b3ed8baad335bbb121.avif?t=1770061582\" width=171 height=123 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与独特的敌人和Boss战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个新区域，你将遇到独特且奇怪的生物，其中大多数生物都想吞噬你。战斗是策略性的，Dahlia和Axo需要研究敌人的模式，并精确掌握技能和时机。游戏中有超过100个敌人，从敏捷的猎人到巨大的怪物，战斗总是充满挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/35d9cd775ef8065d859be70b6149d43a.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/35d9cd775ef8065d859be70b6149d43a.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/35d9cd775ef8065d859be70b6149d43a.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/c688669b34fc15320c0819b9a58f1f9e.avif?t=1770061582\" width=276 height=123 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级Dahlia和Axo的技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索世界时，Dahlia和Axo将遇到各种符文和技能，可以收集、制作、解锁并在战斗中获得。这些将帮助他们提高战斗风格，并根据不同的游戏风格调整他们的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/58df44b9ba5ac876cdb83ebb72467ee3.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/58df44b9ba5ac876cdb83ebb72467ee3.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/58df44b9ba5ac876cdb83ebb72467ee3.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的Discord频道，成为社区的一部分，共同打造最棒的游戏版本。我们可以一起打造一款优秀的Metroidvania，包含更多的生物群落、敌人、NPC、扩展剧情、关卡、Boss、符文、技能等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/56faa0cbb48112801fa17d7854d2914d.poster.avif?t=1770061582\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/56faa0cbb48112801fa17d7854d2914d.webm?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284650/extras/56faa0cbb48112801fa17d7854d2914d.mp4?t=1770061582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注我们以获取更多新闻，随时查看Steam更新！</p>",
